{
    "chapter": 51,
    "verses": {
        "1": {
            "verses": {
                "51:1": {
                    "id": 1
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以扬起土的风盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "2": {
            "verses": {
                "51:2": {
                    "id": 2
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以满载丰富水的云盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "3": {
            "verses": {
                "51:3": {
                    "id": 3
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以海洋中便利航行的船舶盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "4": {
            "verses": {
                "51:4": {
                    "id": 4
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以受命真主而分担众仆事宜的众天使盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "5": {
            "verses": {
                "51:5": {
                    "id": 5
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们的主许诺的清算和报酬确是毋庸置疑的，</p>"
        },
        "6": {
            "verses": {
                "51:6": {
                    "id": 6
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在复活日对众仆的清算是毫无疑问的。</p>"
        },
        "7": {
            "verses": {
                "51:7": {
                    "id": 7
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主以美妙的有轨道的天空盟誓，</p>"
        },
        "8": {
            "verses": {
                "51:8": {
                    "id": 8
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>麦加的人们啊！你们确在相互矛盾的说辞中，你们有时候说“《古兰经》是魔幻”，有时候又说“穆罕默德是魔术师”，还有时候会说“穆罕默德是位诗人”。</p>"
        },
        "9": {
            "verses": {
                "51:9": {
                    "id": 9
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主确知，远离《古兰经》和先知（愿主福安之）的人没有信仰，他是不信道者，是不被引导至正道者。</p>"
        },
        "10": {
            "verses": {
                "51:10": {
                    "id": 10
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>愿这些诽谤《古兰经》及他们的先知之人被弃绝！</p>"
        },
        "11": {
            "verses": {
                "51:11": {
                    "id": 11
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对于后世，他们是愚昧的、忽视的、不注重的。</p>"
        },
        "12": {
            "verses": {
                "51:12": {
                    "id": 12
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们询问：“报酬之日在何时呢？”他们对此一无所知。</p>"
        },
        "13": {
            "verses": {
                "51:13": {
                    "id": 13
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主回答他们说，那是他们在火狱接受惩罚之日。</p>"
        },
        "14": {
            "verses": {
                "51:14": {
                    "id": 14
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>有个声音对他们说：“品尝你们的惩罚吧！这便是曾以此警告过你们，而你们却嘲笑着要求早日实现的惩罚。”</p>"
        },
        "15": {
            "verses": {
                "51:15": {
                    "id": 15
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>复活日，遵从他们的主命令、远离其禁令的敬畏者，必处在诸多流淌的泉水的花园之中，</p>"
        },
        "16": {
            "verses": {
                "51:16": {
                    "id": 16
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>接受他们的主赐予他们的浩荡赏赐，在浩荡赏赐之前的今世他们确是行善者，</p>"
        },
        "17": {
            "verses": {
                "51:17": {
                    "id": 17
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>是坚守夜间礼拜者，他们只睡眠些许时间，</p>"
        },
        "18": {
            "verses": {
                "51:18": {
                    "id": 18
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在凌晨时刻他们祈祷真主饶恕他们的罪过，</p>"
        },
        "19": {
            "verses": {
                "51:19": {
                    "id": 19
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们的钱财中有自愿施舍给乞讨者或因某种原因无法乞讨之人的份额。</p>"
        },
        "20": {
            "verses": {
                "51:20": {
                    "id": 20
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对于笃信真主是创造者和设计者的人，大地上真主所设置其中的山脉、海洋、河流、树木、植物、动物等，均有很多证明真主大能的证据。</p>"
        },
        "21": {
            "verses": {
                "51:21": {
                    "id": 21
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>人们啊！在你们自身中确有很多证明真主大能的证据，难道你们看不见、悟不出吗？</p>"
        },
        "22": {
            "verses": {
                "51:22": {
                    "id": 22
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>天空中有你们今世生活和宗教生活的给养，也有为你们许诺的善与恶。</p>"
        },
        "23": {
            "verses": {
                "51:23": {
                    "id": 23
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>以天地的主盟誓，复活正如你们能发音一样，确是真实的，毋庸置疑的。</p>"
        },
        "24": {
            "verses": {
                "51:24": {
                    "id": 24
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！关于易卜拉欣款待的贵客，天使们的故事来临你了吗？</p>"
        },
        "25": {
            "verses": {
                "51:25": {
                    "id": 25
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当时天使到易卜拉欣跟前说：“祝你平安！”易卜拉欣回答“祝你们平安！”并自言自语的说：我们不认识这些人。</p>"
        },
        "26": {
            "verses": {
                "51:26": {
                    "id": 26
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故他悄悄地到家人跟前，端上一头肥嫩的牛犊，他认为这些只是一些平常的客人。</p>"
        },
        "27": {
            "verses": {
                "51:27": {
                    "id": 27
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>易卜拉欣把那只肥嫩的牛犊递给客人，并温和地对他们说：“你们不吃些为你们呈上的食物吗？”</p>"
        },
        "28": {
            "verses": {
                "51:28": {
                    "id": 28
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当天使们没有吃的时候，易卜拉欣对他们心生恐惧，这时他们为易卜拉欣显现并安慰他说：“不要害怕，我们是真主的使者。”他们向易卜拉欣报喜，说他将得到一个博学之子，即易司哈格（愿主赐其平安）。</p>"
        },
        "29": {
            "verses": {
                "51:29": {
                    "id": 29
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>当他的妻子听到这个喜讯便喊叫着走来，打着自己的脸说：“难道老妇人要生育吗？”她本是位不能生育之人！</p>"
        },
        "30": {
            "verses": {
                "51:30": {
                    "id": 30
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>天使对她说：“我们告诉你的只是你的主所说的，祂所说的绝不会被驳回。”真主对其创造和裁夺确是至睿的，确是至知众仆利益的。</p>"
        },
        "31": {
            "verses": {
                "51:31": {
                    "id": 31
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>易卜拉欣（愿主赐其平安）对天使说：“你们所奉何命？去往何处？”</p>"
        },
        "32": {
            "verses": {
                "51:32": {
                    "id": 32
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>天使回答他说：“真主派遣我们去惩罚一群犯罪者，他们确已犯下最丑陋罪行。</p>"
        },
        "33": {
            "verses": {
                "51:33": {
                    "id": 33
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我们去为他们降下坚硬泥土变成的石头。</p>"
        },
        "34": {
            "verses": {
                "51:34": {
                    "id": 34
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>易卜拉欣啊！那是从你的主那里发出的，以惩治不信道和僭越真主法度的悖逆之人。”</p>"
        },
        "35": {
            "verses": {
                "51:35": {
                    "id": 35
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故我从鲁特族人村中救出所有信道者，使他们免于遭受犯罪者所遭受的惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "36": {
            "verses": {
                "51:36": {
                    "id": 36
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在他们这座村庄里我只发现一家归顺者，他们就是鲁特（愿主赐其平安）的家人。</p>"
        },
        "37": {
            "verses": {
                "51:37": {
                    "id": 37
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我在鲁特族人的村庄留下证明他们受过惩罚的痕迹，以便惧怕遭遇痛苦惩罚的人以此为戒，而不会重蹈覆辙，并获得救赎。</p>"
        },
        "38": {
            "verses": {
                "51:38": {
                    "id": 38
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对惧怕严酷惩罚的人，在穆萨的故事里确有一种迹象，当时我以明显的证据派遣穆萨去劝化法老，</p>"
        },
        "39": {
            "verses": {
                "51:39": {
                    "id": 39
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>法老对此拒绝并以他的力量和军队践踏真理，他评价穆萨（愿主赐其平安）“是个向人们施魔法的魔术师，或是个不知其言的疯子。”</p>"
        },
        "40": {
            "verses": {
                "51:40": {
                    "id": 40
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>故我惩罚了他和他的整个军队，使他们沉溺于海里，将其溺死并毁灭。法老因否认使者并妄称自己是神灵而受到应有的惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "41": {
            "verses": {
                "51:41": {
                    "id": 41
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对惧怕严酷惩罚的人，胡德的宗族的故事里有一种迹象。当时我以飓风毁灭了他们，那风没有带去雨水，也未植下一颗树，其中毫无吉庆。</p>"
        },
        "42": {
            "verses": {
                "51:42": {
                    "id": 42
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>那飓风摧毁了包括人和财物所到之处的一切，只留下一片狼藉。</p>"
        },
        "43": {
            "verses": {
                "51:43": {
                    "id": 43
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>对惧怕严酷惩罚的人，撒立哈（愿主赐其平安）的宗族赛莫德人的故事中确有一种迹象，当时他对族人说：“在生命结束前，你们暂时享受生活吧！”</p>"
        },
        "44": {
            "verses": {
                "51:44": {
                    "id": 44
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他的族人藐视他们的主，不屑于信仰和顺从，故疾雷惩罚了他们，他们眼见惩罚的降临，他们曾在惩罚来临三天前得以警告。</p>"
        },
        "45": {
            "verses": {
                "51:45": {
                    "id": 45
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>他们不能保护自己免遭惩罚，也无力阻挡惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "46": {
            "verses": {
                "51:46": {
                    "id": 46
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>在上述这些人之前，我确已沉溺毁灭了奴哈的宗族，他们是悖逆的民众，故他们应受惩罚。</p>"
        },
        "47": {
            "verses": {
                "51:47": {
                    "id": 47
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我建筑了天空，我以其力量精工雕琢了它，我确实将其拓展。</p>"
        },
        "48": {
            "verses": {
                "51:48": {
                    "id": 48
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我使大地如床一样铺展开适宜人们居住，我确是最优美的铺展者，我为他们铺展了大地。</p>"
        },
        "49": {
            "verses": {
                "51:49": {
                    "id": 49
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我把万物创造成配偶的，就像男性和女性，天空和大地，陆地和海洋。以便你们领悟创造万物两性的真主的独一性，领悟祂的大能。</p>"
        },
        "50": {
            "verses": {
                "51:50": {
                    "id": 50
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你说：“人们啊！你们当以顺从和不违背祂而逃离真主的惩罚奔向祂的奖赏，我对于你们确是真主惩罚的坦率警告者。</p>"
        },
        "51": {
            "verses": {
                "51:51": {
                    "id": 51
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你们不要舍真主而树立另一个神灵去崇拜，对此我确是坦率的警告者。</p>"
        },
        "52": {
            "verses": {
                "51:52": {
                    "id": 52
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>先辈中有象麦加人否认使者一样的民众，每当有位使者从真主那里来临他们，他们必说那使者：“是魔术师或是疯子。”</p>"
        },
        "53": {
            "verses": {
                "51:53": {
                    "id": 53
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>难道之前和之后的不信道者们间相互嘱托否认众使者吗？不然！他们全体都是悖逆的民众。</p>"
        },
        "54": {
            "verses": {
                "51:54": {
                    "id": 54
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！你当回避这些否认使者的人们，你不为此受到责怪，你确已把奉命传达他们的已传达。</p>"
        },
        "55": {
            "verses": {
                "51:55": {
                    "id": 55
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>你回避他们并不能阻碍对他们的劝化，故你当劝化、教诲他们，对于信真主者教诲确是有益的。</p>"
        },
        "56": {
            "verses": {
                "51:56": {
                    "id": 56
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我创造精灵和人类只为他们唯一崇拜我，我创造他们不是为我而树立匹配。</p>"
        },
        "57": {
            "verses": {
                "51:57": {
                    "id": 57
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>我无需他们的给养，也不需他们供养我，</p>"
        },
        "58": {
            "verses": {
                "51:58": {
                    "id": 58
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>真主是供养众仆的，万物只有祈祷祂的给养，祂确是拥有稳固力量的、是不可战胜的，所有精灵和人类都顺服于清高的主的力量。</p>"
        },
        "59": {
            "verses": {
                "51:59": {
                    "id": 59
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>使者啊！因否认你而自欺的不义者和他们之前同类人一样遭遇应受的、有特定期限的惩罚，他们不必求我将惩罚提前。</p>"
        },
        "60": {
            "verses": {
                "51:60": {
                    "id": 60
                }
            },
            "resource_id": 154,
            "resource_name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
            "language_id": 38,
            "slug": "zh_mokhtasar",
            "translated_name": {
                "name": "Tafsir Zh Mokhtasar",
                "language_name": "english"
            },
            "text": "<p>伤哉不信真主、否认其使者的人！当他们被警告的惩罚在复活日来临他们的时候。</p>"
        }
    }
}